title: Talon 9 (Tablet Edition)
description:
This is from the original scanner. I adjusted the resolution and compressed the file for easier reading on tablets and ereaders. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Talon 9

By:   	James TynionIV, Miguel Angel Sepulveda	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Series:   	Talon
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	June 26, 2013
Format:         CBZ

In the aftermath of his encounter with Strix and the Birds of Prey (continuing from this month's BIRDS OF PREY #21), Calvin is sent on his deadliest mission yet: Retrieve one man from the deadliest island on Earth, Santa Prisca, the home of Bane!
